@page "/"

<PageTitle>METERP - Foundation</PageTitle>

<h1>Welcome to METERP</h1>

<p>
    This is the clean foundation for the multi-tenant ERP system (Electrical &amp; Mechanical Contracting, South Africa).
</p>

<p>
    <strong>Current architecture:</strong> Clean Architecture with multi-tenancy built in from day one.
</p>

<ul>
    <li>Domain: BaseEntity + Tenant</li>
    <li>Application: Contracts for tenant management</li>
    <li>Infrastructure: EF Core + global query filters for tenant isolation + soft delete</li>
    <li>Web: Blazor Server</li>
</ul>

<p>
    Next steps in Phase 1: full tenant provisioning, ASP.NET Identity integration with tenant-aware users, permissions, etc.
</p>
